    <item>
      <title>首席经济顾问称印度将通过金融市场看到特朗普关税影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/us-tariffs-to-impact-india-s-financial-markets-adviser-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度首席经济顾问 V Anantha Nageswaran 表示，印度将通过金融市场感受到美国对加拿大、墨西哥和中国的关税影响。他还告诉彭博电视台，印度在制定预算时考虑到了“非常高”的全球不确定性。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/us-tariffs-to-impact-india-s-financial-markets-adviser-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 04:58:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税导致汽车和墨西哥相关股票成为亚洲最大输家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/here-are-the-winners-and-losers-in-asia-from-trump-s-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普启动第一波关税，标志着新一轮全球贸易战的开始，依赖出口的亚洲股市——从日本汽车制造商到中国电子商务公司——暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/here-are-the-winners-and-losers-in-asia-from-trump-s-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 03:49:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受印度降息预期影响，卢比将延续跌势至历史低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/rupee-set-to-extend-slump-to-new-record-on-india-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度卢比兑美元汇率周一创下新低，预计未来将进一步走弱，因为有迹象表明印度央行在新行长领导下将放松对货币的控制，交易员押注央行将降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/rupee-set-to-extend-slump-to-new-record-on-india-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度债券多头押注降息以抵消更高的借款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/bulls-bet-on-rbi-cuts-to-extend-bond-gains-despite-higher-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度债券交易员忽视了周六预算中宣布的债务供应量的小幅增加，因为对本周降息的希望有助于该国债务延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/bulls-bet-on-rbi-cuts-to-extend-bond-gains-despite-higher-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 01:24:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>滞胀风险导致美国国债收益率曲线自 11 月以来最趋平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/treasuries-fall-on-short-end-as-tariffs-deepen-inflation-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对主要贸易伙伴加征关税的举动可能导致经济陷入滞胀，美国国债收益率曲线创下 11 周以来的最大平缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/treasuries-fall-on-short-end-as-tariffs-deepen-inflation-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 01:14:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走强抵消避险需求，黄金下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/gold-edges-higher-as-trump-tariffs-unsettle-global-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对来自加拿大、墨西哥和中国的进口商品征收关税后，金价下跌，因为在全球准备应对贸易战的情况下，美元飙升超过了避险需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/gold-edges-higher-as-trump-tariffs-unsettle-global-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 23:08:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：特朗普关税导致美元上涨、股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普兑现对加拿大、墨西哥和中国进口产品征收关税的威胁后，美元飙升，而股票市场和数字货币暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 22:25:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
